---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import Layout from "../shared/layout/base-layout.astro";
import homePicture from '../shared/pic.jpg';
---
<Layout>
    <div class="prose dark:prose-invert break-words">
        <p class="text-lg leading-8">Community-driven information site about third-party replacement car screens running Android software from KSW and ZXW vendors, for car brands like Audi, Benz, BMW, Mini and others.</p>
        <p>Read about changes found in latest firmware updates, browse through available themes and more. Start by selecting your vendor from the menu.</p>
        <p>Join the conversation on <a href="https://discord.gg/Ex8e6qE2eR">Android Automotive Headunits Discord</a> or various forums like <a href="https://f30.bimmerpost.com/forums/showthread.php?t=1832178">Bimmerpost and its Android 11/12/13 thread</a>.</p>
    </div>
    <Image class="mt-12 rounded-md" src={homePicture} alt="" />
</Layout>
